{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"e2984b4c-fdc3-5b90-896f-4e36a4594545","excerpt":"StackNavigator 在 navigationOptions 里修改 headerStyle TabNavigator 在 tabBarOptions 修改 style 代码 最好在 navigator 定义时设置 navigationOptions…","html":"<ol>\n<li>\n<p>StackNavigator<br>\n在<code>navigationOptions</code>里修改<code>headerStyle</code></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>TabNavigator<br>\n在<code>tabBarOptions</code>修改<code>style</code></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>代码</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre class=\"language-jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\">//Android\nelevation：0\n//iOS\nshadowOpacity：0</code></pre></div>\n<p>最好在<code>navigator</code>定义时设置<code>navigationOptions</code>，否则在页面嵌套的时候容易冲突，可能设置不起作用</p>","tableOfContents":"","frontmatter":{"date":"March 18, 2018","title":"React-Navigation中去掉header下的阴影","image":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.5056179775280898,"src":"/static/9983387778f1c70c0ce32374522d12c6/d7b72/post-default-bg.jpg","srcSet":"/static/9983387778f1c70c0ce32374522d12c6/2347c/post-default-bg.jpg 750w,\n/static/9983387778f1c70c0ce32374522d12c6/5a448/post-default-bg.jpg 1500w,\n/static/9983387778f1c70c0ce32374522d12c6/d7b72/post-default-bg.jpg 3000w,\n/static/9983387778f1c70c0ce32374522d12c6/439d2/post-default-bg.jpg 4288w","sizes":"(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/Blog/React-Navigation中去掉header下的阴影/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/Blog/Android键盘遮挡问题/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Android键盘遮挡问题"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/Blog/RN Animated API使用/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"RN Animated API使用"}}}}